            <div class="support-cards">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>About Us</h3>
                    <p>What do we aim? Our mission and vision for the art community.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Our Projects</h3>
                    <p>Explore our current and past art initiatives and exhibitions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
