}Important Notes:Image Paths:Replace placeholder image paths (../images/hero-bg.jpg, etc.) with your actual image filesCreate an images folder in your public directoryPayment Gateway Assets:Add eSewa/Khalti logo images to public/images/Update paths in the HTML/CSS accordinglyDark Mode Colors:Adjust the dark theme colors in :root if neededResponsive Tweaks:Test on different devices and adjust breakpoints as neededFullCalendar Styling:The calendar will inherit your theme colors automaticallyTo use this CSS:Create public/css/styles.cssPaste the entire code aboveLink it in your HTML head:htmlCopy<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">Run HTMLThe CSS includes all styles for:Dark/light mode toggleResponsive layoutPayment form stylingEvent calendarAll sections from your HTMLSmooth animations and transitions

cssCopy/* ===== Base Styles ===== */
:root {
  /* Light Theme */
  --primary-light: #1a1a1a;
  --secondary-light: #f5f5f5;
  --accent-light: #e63946;
  --text-light: #333;
  --card-light: #ffffff;
  --background-light: #f8f8f8;

  /* Dark Theme */
  --primary-dark: #f5f5f5;
  --secondary-dark: #1a1a1a;
  --accent-dark: #ff6b6b;
  --text-dark: #f0f0f0;
  --card-dark: #2d2d2d;
  --background-dark: #121212;
}

[data-theme="light"] {
  --primary: var(--primary-light);
  --secondary: var(--secondary-light);
  --accent: var(--accent-light);
  --text: var(--text-light);
  --card: var(--card-light);
  --background: var(--background-light);
}

[data-theme="dark"] {
  --primary: var(--primary-dark);
  --secondary: var(--secondary-dark);
  --accent: var(--accent-dark);
  --text: var(--text-dark);
  --card: var(--card-dark);
  --background: var(--background-dark);
}

* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  background-color: var(--background);
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ===== Navigation ===== */
nav {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 20px 5%;
  z-index: 1000;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

[data-theme="dark"] nav {
  background-color: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.9);
}

.logo {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--primary);
  text-decoration: none;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

.logo img {
  height: 40px;
  margin-right: 10px;
}

.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 30px;
  align-items: center;
}

.nav-links a {
  color: var(--primary);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  position: relative;
}

.nav-links a::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -5px;
  left: 0;
  width: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background-color: var(--accent);
  transition: width 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-links a:hover::after {
  width: 100%;
}

.theme-toggle, .language-toggle {
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 8px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  background-color: var(--card);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ===== Hero Section ===== */
.hero {
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 0 20px;
  background-color: var(--primary-light); /* Dark background regardless of theme */
  color: white;
}

.hero-background {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background-image: url('../images/hero-bg.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  z-index: 1;
  opacity: 0.4;
}

.hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 900px;
  padding: 0 20px;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 6rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: white;
  text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
}

.hero h2 {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  color: white;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  font-style: italic;
  animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.2s forwards;
  opacity: 0;
}

.hero p {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.4s forwards;
  opacity: 0;
}

.scroll-down {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 30px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
  animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 3;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.scroll-down:hover {
  color: var(--accent);
}

/* ===== Preview Cards Section ===== */
.preview-section {
  padding: 100px 5%;
  position: relative;
  background-color: var(--secondary);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.preview-title {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: var(--primary);
}

.preview-container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 30px;
  padding: 30px 0;
  overflow-x: auto;
  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
  scrollbar-width: none;
}

.preview-container::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none;
}

.preview-card {
  min-width: 350px;
  height: 500px;
  scroll-snap-align: start;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  border-radius: 15px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1);
}

.preview-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%);
  z-index: 1;
}

.preview-card-content {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 40px;
  z-index: 2;
  transform: translateY(100px);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1);
}

.preview-card:hover {
  transform: scale(1.03);
}

.preview-card:hover .preview-card-content {
  transform: translateY(0);
  opacity: 1;
}

.preview-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: white;
}

.preview-card p {
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
}

.preview-card .btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 12px 30px;
  background-color: var(--accent);
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 30px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.preview-card .btn:hover {
  background-color: #c1121f;
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

/* ===== About Section ===== */
.about-section {
  padding: 120px 5%;
  background-color: var(--card);
  position: relative;
}

.section-title {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 80px;
  font-size: 2.8rem;
  color: var(--primary);
}

.about-content {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  gap: 60px;
}

.about-text {
  flex: 1;
}

.about-text h3 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  color: var(--primary);
}

.about-text p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  color: var(--text);
}

.about-image {
  flex: 1;
  height: 500px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

.about-image img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.8s ease;
}

.about-image:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* ===== Gallery Section ===== */
.gallery-section {
  padding: 120px 5%;
  background-color: var(--secondary);
}

.gallery-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 25px;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.gallery-item {
  height: 300px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 10px;
  position: relative;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1);
}

.gallery-item img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: all 0.8s ease;
}

.gallery-item:hover {
  transform: translateY(-10px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.gallery-item:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}

/* ===== Donate Section ===== */
.donate-section {
  padding: 120px 5%;
  background-color: var(--primary-light);
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.donate-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background-image: url('../images/donate-bg.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  opacity: 0.2;
  z-index: 1;
}

.donate-container {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}

.donate-section h2 {
  color: white;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.donate-section p {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
}

.donate-options {
  display: flex;
  gap: 15px;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
}

.donate-option {
  padding: 15px 30px;
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  border: 2px solid transparent;
}

.donate-option:hover {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}

.donate-option.active {
  background-color: var(--accent);
  border-color: white;
}

.custom-amount input {
  padding: 15px;
  width: 120px;
  border: none;
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  color: white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-align: center;
}

#donationForm {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 500px;
  background-color: var(--card-dark);
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.form-group {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  text-align: left;
}

.form-group label {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: white;
}

.form-group input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 8px;
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  color: white;
}

#paymentMethods {
  display: flex;
  gap: 15px;
  margin: 25px 0;
  justify-content: center;
}

.payment-method {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.payment-method img {
  height: 30px;
}

.payment-method.active {
  background-color: var(--accent);
}

.submit-btn {
  background-color: var(--accent);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  padding: 16px 40px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  border-radius: 30px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3);
  width: 100%;
}

.submit-btn:hover {
  background-color: #c1121f;
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.4);
}

/* ===== Events Section ===== */
.events-section {
  padding: 120px 5%;
  background-color: var(--card);
}

#calendar {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background-color: var(--card);
  border-radius: 15px;
  padding: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.fc-toolbar-title {
  color: var(--primary) !important;
}

.fc-col-header-cell-cushion {
  color: var(--primary) !important;
}

.fc-daygrid-day-number {
  color: var(--text) !important;
}

/* ===== Contact Section ===== */
.contact-section {
  padding: 120px 5%;
  background-color: var(--secondary);
}

.contact-container {
  display: flex;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  gap: 60px;
}

.contact-info {
  flex: 1;
}

.contact-info h3 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  color: var(--primary);
}

.contact-details {
  margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.contact-details p {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 15px;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--text);
}

.contact-details i {
  color: var(--accent);
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  width: 30px;
  text-align: center;
}

.social-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.social-links a {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  background-color: var(--card);
  border-radius: 50%;
  color: var(--primary);
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.social-links a:hover {
  background-color: var(--accent);
  color: white;
  transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.contact-form {
  flex: 1;
  background-color: var(--card);
  padding: 50px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

.contact-form .form-group label {
  color: var(--primary);
}

.contact-form .form-group input,
.contact-form .form-group textarea {
  background-color: var(--background);
  border: 1px solid var(--secondary);
  color: var(--text);
}

/* ===== Footer ===== */
footer {
  background-color: var(--primary);
  color: white;
  padding: 80px 5% 40px;
}

.footer-content {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 40px;
}

.footer-column h4 {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  color: white;
}

.footer-column p {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
}

.footer-links {
  list-style: none;
}

.footer-links li {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.footer-links a {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.footer-links a:hover {
  color: white;
  padding-left: 5px;
}

.copyright {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 60px;
  padding-top: 30px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

/* ===== Animations ===== */
@keyframes fadeInUp {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

@keyframes bounce {
  0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {
    transform: translateY(0) translateX(-50%);
  }
  40% {
    transform: translateY(-20px) translateX(-50%);
  }
  60% {
    transform: translateY(-10px) translateX(-50%);
  }
}

.animate {
  opacity: 0;
}

.animated {
  animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
}

.delay-1 {
  animation-delay: 0.2s;
}

.delay-2 {
  animation-delay: 0.4s;
}

.delay-3 {
  animation-delay: 0.6s;
}

/* ===== Responsive Design ===== */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .about-content,
  .contact-container {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .about-image {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .contact-form {
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
  }

  .hero h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .nav-links {
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .preview-card {
    min-width: 280px;
    height: 450px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 576px) {
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
  }

  .hero h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: none; /* Consider adding a mobile menu */
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .preview-card {
    min-width: 250px;
    height: 400px;
  }

  .contact-form {
    padding: 30px;
  }

  .donate-options {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .donate-option {
    width: 100%;
  }
}
